Name: Wing Beat
Desc:
Creates a whirlwind that attacks enemies until a fixed number of monsters are killed. The whirlwind will dissipate after a short distance or time. Wing Beat does not cause you to take damage even when attacking enemies in the Damage Reflection Status. Up to 2 can be in place at a time.
Command Skill: During Attack + Jump Key + Command
